1.11 Meta
=========

This specification was written after the fact, reconstructing decisions
from code and usage.  Future decisions should be documented as they’re
made, using the memory layer’s decision trail feature.

   The self-referential nature is intentional: form-copilot helps
complete complex multi-section documents; this specification is a
complex multi-section document about form-copilot.


